InsufficientPrivilegesException.documentation: Unable to perform the specified operation because the user does not have enough privileges for one of more downstream aws services

InvalidRequestException.documentation: The request is invalid, please check parameters and their values

ManagedActionInvalidStateException.documentation: Managed update is not in a valid state to be modified

MissingRequiredResourceException.documentation: Required resources associated with specified parameters are missing.

OperationInProgressException.documentation: Unable to perform the specified operation because another operation is already in progress affecting an element in this activity.

S3LocationNotInServiceRegionException.documentation: The specified S3 bucket does not belong to the S3 region in which the service is running.

S3SubscriptionRequiredException.documentation: The caller does not have a subscription to Amazon S3.

SourceBundleDeletionException.documentation: Unable to delete the Amazon S3 source bundle associated with the application version, although the application version deleted successfully.

TooManyEnvironmentsException.documentation: The caller has exceeded the limit of allowed environments associated with the account.
